{"tid":1845851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有個方法可以重整連登風氣","createTime":"2020-01-27T11:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T12:33:43.000Z","uid":46404,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3549b82c7058ad5abd85156e82c52af6ada8ce37","tid":1845851,"uid":46404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:16:27.000Z","msg":"同打阻膠道理一樣就係自律 我唔知以前有無人提意過<br />\n<br />\n以後有行動前一日既話就所有人開既post都要關於行動當日既內容或者有關既資訊<br />\n<br />\n一律有啲關人撚事既post又或者重複洗版既post大家都唔該block撚左條友 等佢自己一個玩連登 <br />\n<br />\n基本上有一班人只係睇熱門 所以基本上得熱門既關人撚事post都幫手block左佢同幫推既個班撚屌<br />\n但係要靠大家一人做多步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁就可以專注返係行動post到"},{"pid":"df742ca992161d2c72a0fbe97412c981b4fc572a","tid":1845851,"uid":46404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:17:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1015121703e08276536a3cec8be75b5251c6803","tid":1845851,"uid":46404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:18:09.000Z","msg":"呢個年代真係難推"},{"pid":"5dba926861b216047df5650d507e2f2f927851db","tid":1845851,"uid":46404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:18:24.000Z","msg":"連登好的講無人睇咁"},{"pid":"3e3c5c4f12cfd1f9a79ab7bf51b59a1223f0260b","tid":1845851,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:18:25.000Z","msg":"連仔唔理 無計"},{"pid":"ae46bf5d4b175d81b13d322610f938c4217263e6","tid":1845851,"uid":46404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:18:34.000Z","msg":"攰啦"},{"pid":"008af6cb5a60d972725dde30082b912e0d0262d7","tid":1845851,"uid":46404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e3c5c4f12cfd1f9a79ab7bf51b59a1223f0260b","tid":1845851,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:18:25.000Z","msg":"連仔唔理 無計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:18:59.000Z","msg":"佢無得出手既 亂來又比人屌"},{"pid":"e4adc85d1d3be7c4222d572d247fc2d23a041d62","tid":1845851,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0